<div class="story"><p>Admirals View III is an ocean front condominium development in Kill Devil Hills with a total of 18 individual units with 6 units on each of 3 levels. Every unit has 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths with on-site laundry facilities. The master bedroom and living room face the ocean with glass sliding doors that open up onto an ocean facing deck. The floor plan is open through the kitchen, dining area and living area creating one long room with views possible from most of the area. Admirals View III is  on RT. 12 in Kill Devil Hills just north of the subdivision <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KillDevilHills/kill-devil-beach.asp" title="Kill Devil Beach">Kill Devil Beach</a>.</p>
